I can’t believe my little girl is already 8 years old today🤧

Up to 196lbs now and have actually done really well on the start of this bulk!

This is by far the best I’ve ever looked at this weight! Usually when I start a bulk I just instantly switch to the “eat everything and gain as much weight as I can” mindset. 

I really wanted to do the opposite on this bulk because when I eat fast food/junk constantly I feel bad about my self because I have no structure and I also just physically feel bad! (Not to mention it’s harder to get more food in when you eat heavy greasy meals) 
 
Excited to keep getting stronger and keep improving 😈

If you want to train with me the links are in my bio.
